<br>
All hype the truth is<br>
<br>
Ok the Graphics are awesome can't lie but player interaction is just like Diablo II.  Where everyone screws everyone over and duping will be common.  Updates to the entire game will be difficult with people creating there own worlds.  And when you complete your world what are the chances you have bugs and or bad polygons.  I know cause I made modules for Marthon II, Marthon Infinity, and Half-Life.  And they were bugged like no other.  This will be the same way.  So the hype for this game was much greater than the game.<br>
